== HashAccess

HashAccess library allows access to hash elements by calling methods.

=== Installation

The latest source

 git clone https://github.com/slavach/hash-access.git

The old version

 gem install hash-access

=== Usage example

 require './lib/hash_access.rb'
 include HashAccess

 h = {}
 h.access_by_methods
 h.first_key = 'First value'
 h.another_key = 'Another value'

